title: Starsiege Tribes 1.11  -  Fully patched XP/Vista compatible
description:
This is a full copy of a Tribes1 directory that has been
installed and patched to version 1.11(the last patch).

To install, simply extract StarsiegeTribes111.rar and you&#039;re set.
To play, just run Tribes.exe. 

Vista users will need to use T1Vista.exe instead of Tribes.exe.
This has been tested on Vista Premium 64 and XP Pro SP2
for both local and online multiplayer. There is still a decent
population of active players online, so join in!
